comments.body:
@matthewjchandler Last week we merged a PR that enhanced a little bit the data entry for read-only and read-write users: https://github.com/pulibrary/tiger-data-app/pull/236 so that the data entry mimics what we do in PDC Describe.

It does not do auto-complete based on the netid yet, but it is moving us on the right direction.

Not shown in the referenced screenshot is that there is also a "delete" icon next to each user added so user can delete remove individual users from the role.
